Package: a11ytables
Title: Create Spreadsheet Publications Following GSS Best Practice
Version: 0.0.0.9004
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Matt",
           family = "Dray",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "mattdray@gmail.com")
Description: Generate spreadsheet publications for official release by UK
    government following best practice guidance from the UK's Government 
    Statistical Service (GSS), with a focus on accessibility for all users.
    Based on {openxlsx}. See also the Python package 'gptables' by the Best 
    Practice and Impact Division.
URL: https://github.com/co-analysis/a11ytables
BugReports: https://github.com/co-analysis/a11ytables/issues
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.1.2
Depends: 
    R (>= 2.10)
Imports: 
    openxlsx
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    covr
Config/testthat/edition: 3
